title: 02/15/21 – Hour 2 – Carson Wentz Isn’t Worth The Eagles’ Asking Price. Guest – Albert Breer
itunes:title: 02/15/21 – Hour 2 – Carson Wentz Isn’t Worth The Eagles’ Asking Price. Guest – Albert Breer
description:
Jason Smith and Doug Gottlieb sit in for Dan Patrick and weigh in on the latest trade rumors surrounding Carson Wentz and question if the Texans are making the appropriate moves to keep their franchise quarterback (Deshaun Watson). Plus, the guys chat with The MMQB’s Senior NFL Reporter Albert Breer about which quarterbacks will be on the move this offseason!.
